_sText:
de_zenith is a port of the de_zenith from the Counter-Strike: Global Offensive game.

BACKGROUND: 

Recent large scale impact in southern Europe has initiated collaboration among astronomic institutes to prevent such events happening in the future. 

Opposing organisations are threatening these efforts for taking focus away form the ongoing economical and envrionmental crysis within the continent. 

26th November 2023 - Fire fight breaks out between security members and a group of armed men at high altitude observatory Zenith. 

The new S.S.G. prototype modules could be at risk from the attack.
